      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "8. Crankshaft main bearing removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "9. Crankshaft Main Bearing Inspection"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "387_3.0_jpn_11582904_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "Measurements must always be taken in the axial direction.",
        "Do not rotate the crankshaft."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "4",
      "text": "Install the main bearing, bearing cap, and bearing cap bridge, and tighten the bearing cap bolts in numerical order to 33 N-m (3.4 kgf-m)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "387_3.0_jpn_11582905_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "5",
      "text": "Remove the bearing cap bridge, bearing cap, and main bearing, and measure the crushed width of the plastigage with the scale printed on the bag of the plastigage."
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "Measurements should be taken at the most widely crimped point.",
        "If the limit is exceeded, inspect the cylinder block for enlargement and journal wear, and if there are no abnormalities, replace the bearing with an undersized bearing according to the main bearing identification chart and measure the oil clearance again."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "rows": [
        [
          {
            "text": "No. 1, 4 Journal",
            "colspan": 2
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "text": "Std."
          },
          {
            "text": "0.013－0.029mm"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "text": "Limit value: 1"
          },
          {
            "text": "0.037mm"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "text": "No. 2, 3 Journal",
            "colspan": 2
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "text": "Std."
          },
          {
            "text": "0.017－0.033mm"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "text": "Limit value: 1"
          },
          {
            "text": "0.041mm"
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "387_3.0_jpn_11582906_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "6",
      "text": "Examine the mating marks on the cylinder block."
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "If the mating mark is not visible, do not scrub with a wire brush, screwdriver, etc., but clean with washing oil, etc., and check."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "rows": [
        [
          {
