      "text": "Examine the mating marks on the crankshaft main journal."
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "If the mating mark is not visible, do not scrub with a wire brush, screwdriver, etc., but clean with washing oil, etc., and check."
      ]
